---
title: Nectarine and Zucchini Panzanella with Toasted Crouton and White Wine Vinaigrette
description: What’s not to like about a salad that’s equal parts bread and veggies? This panzanella gets its gusto from thinly shaved zucchini, fresh mozzarella, and a juicy, sweet nectarine. Unlike most salads, this one is even better if made a few hours in advance. Just toss the arugula and mint in right before serving.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nectarine-and-zucchini-panzanella-84c771e8.jpg
